* ServerBootstrap and Bootstrap
* EventLoopGroup -> NioEventLoopGroup
* SimpleChannelInboundHandler vs ChannelInboundHandlerAdapter
* ChannelPipeline -> DefaultChannelPipeline
* Bootstrap diff ServerBootstrap
* ChannelInboundHandler and ChannelOutboundHandler <-- ChannelHandler
* ChannelHandlerContext
* 适配器：
    ChannelHandlerAdapter ChannelInboundHandlerAdapter ChannelOutboundHandlerAdapter
* EventExecutor
* SimpleChannelInboundHandler diff ChannelInboundHandler
* ByteBuf ByteBufHolder
* ByteBuf
    堆缓冲区
    直接缓冲区 <- 内存池
    复合缓冲区 CompositeByteBuf
* Pooled和Unpooled
* ByteBufAllocator
* ChannelHandlerContext


10个核心类：
 Bootstrap or ServerBootstrap 
 EventLoop
 EventLoopGroup
 ChannelPipeline
 Channel
 Future or ChannelFuture 
 ChannelInitializer
 ChannelHandler


Bootstrap 用来连接远程主机，有 1 个 EventLoopGroup  
ServerBootstrap 用来绑定本地端口，有 2 个 EventLoopGroup


io.netty.channel.socket.nio
io.netty.channel.socket.oio
io.netty.channel.local
io.netty.channel.embedded
     OIO，在低连接数、需要低延迟时、阻塞时使用
     NIO，在高连接数时使用
     Local，在同一个 JVM 内通信时使用
     Embedded，测试 ChannelHandler 时使用


